      <title>法院规则司法部可以重新审理房地产经纪人案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/justice-department-can-reopen-realtors-case-appeals-court-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上诉法院周五裁定，司法部可以重新启动对全国房地产经纪人协会的反垄断调查，驳回该房地产贸易组织执行 2020 年与特朗普政府达成的和解协议以结案的请求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/justice-department-can-reopen-realtors-case-appeals-court-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 14:29:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
